---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">
  <section class="mt-24 mb-32">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-bold leading-none tracking-tighter mb-8">
      PAULA MÉNDEZ ORTEGA<br/>
      <span class="text-white/20 italic">モップ アーカイブ</span>
    </h1>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mt-16">
      <div class="text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
        <p class="mb-4">
          [KR] 디지털 아키텍트와 창의적 코딩을 통해 시각적 경험을 구축합니다.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/50">
          Digital architect focused on building immersive visual experiences through creative coding and structural design.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-end items-end italic text-xs text-white/30">
        <p>BASED IN MEXICO</p>
        <p>AVAILABLE GLOBALLY</p>
        <p>WORKING ON: KODŌ PROJECT, K-TREND ANALYZER</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-white/10 pt-12 mt-12">
  <p class="text-[10px] text-white/40 mb-12 tracking-[0.3em]">SELECTED ARCHIVE / 2026</p>
  
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
    <a href="/kodo" class="group flex flex-col gap-4">
      <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-white/5 overflow-hidden relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] text-white/20 group-hover:text-white/60 transition-colors">
          [ IMAGE_PREVIEW_KODO ]
        </div>
        </div>
      <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold">KODŌ PROJECT</h3>
        <span class="text-[10px] text-white/30 italic">STRUCTURAL DESIGN / AI</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/k-trend" class="group flex flex-col gap-4">
      <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-white/5 overflow-hidden relative border border-white/5 group-hover:border-white/20 transition-all">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] text-white/20 group-hover:text-white/60">
          [ IMAGE_PREVIEW_KTREND ]
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold">K-TREND ANALYZER</h3>
        <span class="text-[10px] text-white/30 italic">DATA VISUALIZATION / KR</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
